    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! You've seriously got to see this beauty in person. It's in absolutely stunning, mint condition\u2014honestly, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's been pampered since day one, spotless inside and out, and drives like a dream. If you're looking for perfection, this is the one. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
