      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a true collector-grade vehicle that has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment. The exterior retains its deep, factory-original luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating with absolutely zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom state; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, the carpets are pristine, and the interior still carries that distinct new-car aroma. Every electronic component, from the precision-tuned audio system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio documenting every scheduled maintenance interval performed by factory-trained technicians. With a spotless undercarriage and a smooth, responsive powertrain, this vehicle offers a driving experience indistinguishable from the day it was first delivered. This is a turn-key investment for the discerning enthusiast who accepts nothing less than perfection.",
